{"full_title_en": "COVID-19 Inpatient Risk Calculator (CIRC)", "instructions_en": "", "search_abbreviation_en": ["COVID Inpatient Risk Calculator, COVID, coronavirus, covid mortality, covid death, covid progression, covid-19, coronavirus mortality, coronavirus progression, covid death risk, covid death, covid mortality risk, covid progression risk"], "calc_type": "calculator", "before_use": "<p>This calculator includes inputs based on race, which may or may not provide better estimates; this calculator cannot be run without the &ldquo;White Yes/No&rdquo; answer. Non-white patients tend to have higher mortalities in this score.&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" data-stringify-link=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/race\" delay=\"150\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/race\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">See here</a>&nbsp;for more on our approach to addressing race and bias on MDCalc.</p>\n<p>Launched during COVID-19 crisis. Not externally validated. Use with caution.</p>", "cmeLastReviewed": null, "purpose_en": ["Prognosis"], "specialty_en": ["Critical Care", "Emergency Medicine", "Hospitalist Medicine", "Infectious Disease", "Internal Medicine", "Pulmonology"], "slug": "covid-19-inpatient-risk-calculator-circ", "disease_en": ["Coronavirus", "COVID-19"], "cmeEndDate": null, "short_description_en": "Inpatient COVID mortality or severe disease progression.", "short_title_en": "CIRC", "medium_description_en": "Predicts likelihood of inpatient mortality or severe disease progression in COVID patients.", "input_schema": [{"optional": false, "default": null, "unit": "age", "conditionality": "", "name": "age", "tips_en": "", "label_en": "<p>Age</p>", "type": "textbox", "unit_info": {"name": "Age", "conversion": 1, "error_min": 0.001, "error_max": 120, "warn_min": 0.1, "warn_max": 100, "normal_max_si": 0, "normal_min_si": 0, "normal_min_us": 0, "units_si": "years", "units_us": "years"}}, {"optional": false, "default": null, "show_points": false, "conditionality": "", "n